##  EXEMPLO DE `.nc/config.yaml` (COMPLETO)

```yaml
# .nc/config.yaml
# Configuraes locais para projeto "turboquant"

logging:
  level: DEBUG
  file: logs/neocortex.log  # relativo ao projeto

metrics:
  enabled: true
  port: 9091                 # porta diferente da global

hooks:
  enabled: true
  directory: .nc/hooks/
  pre_tool_use:
    - matcher: "Edit"
      script: .nc/hooks/check-ssot.py
    - matcher: "Write"
      script: .nc/hooks/validate-naming.py

plugins:
  enabled: true
  auto_discovery: true
  directory: .nc/plugins/

policies:
  max_tokens_per_task: 50000
  max_tasks_per_session: 10

session_mate:
  enable_avatars: true
  enable_achievements: false

# Campos @LOCKED (sero ignorados no merge)
atomic_locks:
  enabled: false   #  IGNORADO, mantm true global
```

